data.title: Jacqueline Wayland, Real Estate Agent
data.meta_description: Jacqueline Wayland is a Coldwell Banker Realty real estate agent serving Concord, MA and the surrounding areas.
data.text:
I am a full-time agent that is motivated to help people with their real estate needs. I have extensive knowledge of the area. This knowledge coupled with my background in customer service, business and education aids in the high quality service that I extend to my clients. With dedication and a caring demeanor I will always put your best interests first throughout the real estate process. Whether you are looking to rent, buy, sell or invest I will help you achieve your real estate goals.

If you're looking for a positive, helpful partner who is ready to provide you with exceptional service, let's talk today!

I look forward to meeting you! Be well and be safe!
